<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Healthcare Staff Portal | Login</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    * {
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f7fa;
      color: #333;
    }
    
    .container {
      display: flex;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    
    .left-panel {
      flex: 1;
      background-image: url('https://img.freepik.com/free-photo/medical-workers-studying-together_23-2149271066.jpg');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      position: relative;
      display: none;
    }
    
    .overlay {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      background: rgba(25, 118, 210, 0.8);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      color: white;
    }
    
    .left-content {
      max-width: 80%;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    
    .left-content h2 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .left-content p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    
    .feature {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    
    .feature i {
      margin-right: 10px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
    
    .right-panel {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    
    .login-container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 400px;
      padding: 2rem;
      background-color: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    
    .logo-container {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    
    .logo {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      margin-right: 10px;
    }
    
    .logo-text {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #1976d2;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: #333;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    
    .login-description {
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    
    form {
      width: 100%;
      border: none;
      padding: 0;
      height: auto;
    }
    
    .input-group {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .input-group i {
      position: absolute;
      left: 10px;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      color: #666;
    }
    
    input {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px 12px 12px 40px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    }
    
    input:focus {
      border-color: #1976d2;
      outline: none;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(25, 118, 210, 0.2);
    }
    
    input::placeholder {
      color: #999;
    }
    
    button {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px;
      background-color: #1976d2;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    
    button:hover {
      background-color: #1565c0;
    }
    
    .instructions {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      padding: 1rem;
      background-color: #f0f7ff;
      border-radius: 5px;
      border-left: 4px solid #1976d2;
    }
    
    .instructions p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #333;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .footer {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #777;
    }
    
    .help-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      color: #1976d2;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .left-panel {
        display: block;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="left-panel">
      <div class="overlay">
        <div class="left-content">
          <h2>Welcome to HealthConnect Staff Portal</h2>
          <p>Access everything you need to provide exceptional patient care in one secure place.</p>
          
          <div class="feature">
            <i class="fas fa-user-md"></i>
            <span>Patient records and medical history</span>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i>
            <span>Appointment scheduling and management</span>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <i class="fas fa-clipboard-list"></i>
            <span>Treatment plans and medication tracking</span>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i>
            <span>Analytics and reporting tools</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="right-panel">
      <div class="login-container">
        <div class="logo-container">
          <img src="https://img.freepik.com/free-vector/hospital-logo-design-vector-medical-cross_53876-136743.jpg" alt="HealthConnect Logo" class="logo">
          <div class="logo-text">Instabed</div>
        </div>
        
        <h1>Hospital Staff Login</h1>
        <p class="login-description">Enter your hospital ID to access the secure staff portal.</p>
        
        <form action="/sLogin" method="post">
          <div class="input-group">
            <i class="fas fa-hospital-user"></i>
            <input type="text" name="hospital_id" placeholder="Enter Your Hospital ID..." required autofocus>
          </div>
          
          <button type="submit">Enter Portal</button>
        </form>
        
        <div class="instructions">
          <p><strong>Your hospital ID:</strong> The unique identifier assigned to you by your hospital administration.</p>
          <p>If you don't know your ID or need assistance, please contact your department supervisor.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© 2025 HealthConnect. All rights reserved.</p>
        <a href="#" class="help-link">Need help? Contact support</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>